code: class MemoryCache{constructor(){this.cache=void 0;this.cache=new Map();}get(key,ttl){const item=this.cache.get(key);if(!item)return null;const now=Date.now();if(now-item.timestamp>ttl){this.cache.delete(key);return null;}return item.value;}set(key,value){this.cache.set(key,{value,timestamp:Date.now()});}clear(){this.cache.clear();}}export const memoryCache=new MemoryCache();
